The Law of the People's Republic of China on the Construction of a Barrier-Free Environment stipulates that public service places should be equipped with necessary barrier-free facilities and assistive devices, with signage guiding barrier-free facilities, to provide barrier-free services for people with disabilities and the elderly.  

